=================================
 Bkleaner - Book cleaner utility
=================================

Change stylesheets of ebooks in EPUB format.

Installation
============

To install locally using Python::

  python setup.py sdist
  pip install -r requirements.txt
  pip install dist/bkleaner-0.1.tar.gz --user

To uninstall::

  pip uninstall bkleaner

Dependancies
============

Dependancies can be found in the file `requirements.txt`. Whole code
has been tested under Python 3.

